data.description: Looking for that rare gem of a house in Glenwood on 1.25 acres! Beautiful property, quiet community, with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath brick home!! This home has two living rooms, and a garage shower. Over $40,000 of upgrades in the last year, including all new flooring, fixtures, new HVAC system, new well pump, new storage shed.     This is the perfect home for entertaining indoors or outdoors. Backyar boasts fruit trees and low maintenance flowers – an outdoor Florida oasis! The perfect place to relax and listen to the peaceful sounds of nature in this quiet and serene neighborhood. It is surrounded by a new fence. Ideally located in Central Florida, within an hour of major airports and the east coast beaches, Ormond, Daytona, or New Smyrna, as well as Orlando, the Ocala National Forest, the St. John's River. You will certainly not run out of enjoyable options nearby! Deland has a great downtown with a variety of shops and restaurants, as well as grocery, clothing, pet, automotive, hospital, and most other amenities you can think of. In addition, there are parks, such as Deleon Springs, nature walks, and bike trails that you can access from this home.
